      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get the race condition thing. but honestly, it's driving the devs crazy because it's so inconsistent. one minute everything is fine, the next the whole thing just breaks for no obvious reason. it's like the system is just sabotaging itself. does it ever happen where things just go sideways for no reason at all, like some kind of hidden glitch?",
